This paper belongs to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category as it focuses on how users interact with different mobile devices. The paper also involves data analysis and regression analysis, which could fall under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the usage of different mobile devices, which could be related to Multimedia (cs.MM) and Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-categories. However, the focus on user behavior and device substitution makes cs.HC the most likely sub-category.
